{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/dev/web/web,network","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ab75622c-863a-59f4-a67c-efd6a9b03704","html":"<h1 id=\"슈퍼개발자-춤추는망고입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-%EC%B6%A4%EC%B6%94%EB%8A%94%EB%A7%9D%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"슈퍼개발자 춤추는망고입니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>슈퍼개발자, 춤추는망고입니다.</h1>\n<p>( <del>춤 안춥니다.</del> )</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"인터넷에-대한-이해\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%ED%84%B0%EB%84%B7%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4\" aria-label=\"인터넷에 대한 이해 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인터넷에 대한 이해!</h2>\n<h1 id=\"웹의-역사와-발전-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%9D%98-%EC%97%AD%EC%82%AC%EC%99%80-%EB%B0%9C%EC%A0%84-\" aria-label=\"웹의 역사와 발전  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>웹의 역사와 발전 !</h1>\n<p><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"웹이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"웹이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>웹이란?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">웹 ( Web ) - 거미줄</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">월드 와이드 웹 (WWW) 의 줄임말이에요!\n\n&#39; 네트워크 &#39; 상에서 컴퓨터 간의 상호작용을 하는 시스템이죠!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"네트워크란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%84%A4%ED%8A%B8%EC%9B%8C%ED%81%AC%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"네트워크란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>네트워크란?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">네트 ( Net ) - 그물\n워크 ( Work ) - 일\n\n여러 선들이 그물처럼 엮여있는 모양이 떠오르죠?</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">원래 뜻은 그물을 짜는 행위였지만,\n임의의 연결망을 지칭하는 용어로 더 자주 쓰이고 있어요 !</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"사실-컴퓨터는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%8B%A4-%EC%BB%B4%ED%93%A8%ED%84%B0%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"사실 컴퓨터는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>사실, 컴퓨터는</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1940년대에 존 폰노이만, 엘런튜링과 같은 공학자들이\n계산하는 일을 시키기위해 만든 기계였는데요.\n\n공학자들은 더 수준높은 계산을 더 잘하기위해,\n이런 기계들을 연결하여 각 기계들이 할 일을 분담했어요.\n\n서로 계산할 내용을 &quot;통신&quot; 한거죠!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"-정보를-주고-받는-것--이-주된-목적이였기-때문에\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B3%A0-%EB%B0%9B%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%83--%EC%9D%B4-%EC%A3%BC%EB%90%9C-%EB%AA%A9%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B4%EC%98%80%EA%B8%B0-%EB%95%8C%EB%AC%B8%EC%97%90\" aria-label=\" 정보를 주고 받는 것  이 주된 목적이였기 때문에 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>’ 정보를 주고 받는 것 ’ 이 주된 목적이였기 때문에,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">초기 네트워크는 매우 단순했고,\n\n주고 받는 문서의 모양새도 아주 단순했어요.</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"그리고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B7%B8%EB%A6%AC%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"그리고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>그리고,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1973년 TCP/IP 라는 개념을 정립한 빈튼 서프와 밥 간이\n\n&#39;네트워크의 네트워크&#39;\n\n를 구현하여, 모든 컴퓨터를 하나의 통신망 안에 연결하고자 했는데요.</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">이 때 등장한 용어가\n\nInternational Network.\n\n그리고 이 용어의 줄임말이 인터넷(Internet)이에요!</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/dev/web/web,network","tagSlugs":["/tag/web/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-25","description":"웹과 네트워크에 대한 글입니다.","tags":["web"],"title":"웹? 네트워크?","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/dev/web/web,network"}}}